  <brief_title>A Predictive Model for Inadequate Bowel Preparation Before Colonoscopy: Development and Validation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Predictive Model for Inadequate Bowel Preparation Before Colonoscopy: Development and Validation</official_title>
